resources.description: As new engine of economic development, cultural industry is taken as the fourth wave of economic power following the information industry and has become a pillar industry of national economy in many developed countries. To correctly understand the inherent characteristics of cultural industries, deeply analyze the competitive elements of cultural industries, and identify advantages, short board and constraints of cultural industry development in Inner Mongolia will help us take targeted effective measures, which has vital significance for promoting healthy and rapid development of Inner Mongolia culture industry and improving the competitiveness of the industry of culture.
resources.name: Research on Inner Mongolia Cultural Industrial Competitiveness Based on Industry Characteristics
